 opener"><span class="TextRun Underlined SCXW161449428 BCX0" lang="EN-US" 
 xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none">Students\, sign up here &gt\;</span
 ></a></span></p><p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW161449428 BCX0">Clark A
 boud is a composer and producer with a fascination for all styles and sou
 nds. That love for a range of genres finds its way into all of Clark's mu
 sic\, whether blending ominous orchestral colors with unique synths in th
 e hit indie game Slay the Spire\, in the mix of sampling\, lo-fi synths &
 amp\; beats for the BAFTA winning Kind Words (lo fi chill beats to write 
 to)\, or bringing retro-console synths</span><span class="NormalTextRun S
 CXW161449428 BCX0">and ambience to the critically acclaimed VIDEOVERSE.</
 span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW161449428 BCX0"></span><span class="N
 ormalTextRun SCXW161449428 BCX0">Alongside writing for short films and an
 imation\, Clark has contributed to a short for HBO's Sesame Street\, and 
 provided underscore for programs on VICE\, NBC\, MTV\, Discovery\, Animal
  Planet\, Bravo &amp\; others.</span></p>
