 n Person Only    Sponsored by the IU Office of the Chancellor  The summit
  provides an opportunity to wrestle with questions about authorship\, own
 ership\, environmental impact\, cultural disruption\, business transforma
 tion\, and the meaning of creativity itself.  Primary partners for this p
 roject are the Maurer School of Law\, IU Innovates\, Music Tectonics\, an
 d the AI+Digital Futures Team.  AlgoRhythms is generously supported by Fr
 ank Graves\, whose contributions to the Jacobs School of Music and Indian
