SUMMARY:AlgoRhythms: A Summit on AI and Human-Centered Creativity
DESCRIPTION:SATURDAY\, MARCH 28All events in Sweeney Hall\, IU Jacobs Sch
 ool of Music| Zoom and YouTube Live  Note: Additional events are on Thurs
 day and Friday. See Website for details.&#160\;CONFERENCE WEBSITE (https:
 //blogs.iu.edu/jsominnovation/algorhythms-the-world-of-music-and-ai/) |&#
