 /><strong>Repertoire</strong><br />  Beethoven: <em>Piano Trio in E-Flat 
 Major\, Op. 1 No. 1 (1795)<br /></em>L. Boulanger: <em>Deux pi├©ces en tr
 io (1917)<br /></em>R. Schumann: <em>Piano Trio No. 1 in D Minor\, Op. 63
  (1847)<br /></em><br /><strong>About the Artists</strong><br /><br />  C
 ombining the talents of three award-winning soloists\, the <strong>Weiss 
