 n's 32 piano sonatas. An advocate for the power of music in the service o
 f peace\, she is a frequent guest on national and international media. We
 iss is a graduate of the Peabody Conservatory and Mannes College\, where 
 she studied with Leon Fleisher and Richard Goode.<br /></p> Meeting URL: 
