 quot\;left&quot\;,&quot\;469777804&quot\;:&quot\;’éĘ&quot\;,&quot\;469777
 815&quot\;:&quot\;hybridMultilevel&quot\;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-p
 osinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="none">Space is avail
 able for the first 12 people to check in with Guest Services on the day. 
 Drop by the information desk on the first floor of the museum when you ar
 rive.</span></li></ul><ul><li data-leveltext="’éĘ" data-font="Symbol" dat
